cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DL. 

The paper proposes a novel method for data augmentation using deep reinforcement learning, which is a popular technique in the field of machine learning and falls under the category of deep learning (cs.LG). The proposed method is evaluated on various benchmark datasets related to computer vision (cs.CV) and image classification (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a hybrid architecture of dueling deep Q-learning algorithm and a surrogate deep model, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and deep learning (cs.DL).
